Terraform commands :
*****************************
1. Check the version

 command : terraform version

2.Intilaizing the terraform working directory and downloads the required plugins

 command : terraform init

3.Checks whether the Terraform configuration files are syntactically correct.

 command : terraform validate

4.Formate terraform confuguration files

 command : terraform fmt

5.Shows the executaion plan before creating and modifying resources

 command : terraform plan

6.Creates or updates infrastructure based on Terraform configuration
 
 command : terraform apply

7.Display the current stage of managed infastructure

 command : terraform show

8.Display the output vlaues defined terraform confuriguation

 command : terraform output

9.List all resources managed by terraform 

 command : terraform state list

10.Delete all resources managed by terraform

 command :terraform destory

11.List all avaliable workspaces

 command : terraform workspace list

12.Create a new workspace

 command : terraform workspace new <workspace-name>